Package nl.tudelft.dnainator.graph.impl.query

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Query<T>
    The Query represents a query that can be executed on the database.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllClustersQuery
    The AllClustersQuery creates Clusters from all nodes, starting at the startNodes, and ending when the maximum specified start rank is reached.
    ClusterEvaluator
    Evaluates whether a node is part of a cluster based on the given threshold.
    ClusterQuery
    The ClusterQuery creates one single Cluster from all nodes, starting at the start, that have a base sequence shorter than the specified threshold.
    ClustersFromQuery
    The ClustersFromQuery creates multiple Clusters from all nodes, starting at a list of startNodes, that have a base sequence shorter than the specified threshold.
